  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    APN
    A set of parameters used to hand over to the Access Point Name (APN) configuration related methods of the CASIO Enterprise Developer Tools:
    APN.Builder
    Provides a convenient way to set the fields of a APN object when creating a new instance, following the Builder pattern.
    ApplicationInfo
    Application information class for use in KeyLibrary methods
    ReadWriteFileParams
    A set of parameters used to hand over to the readFile and writeFile methods of the CASIO Enterprise Developer Tools
    ReadWriteFileParams.Builder
    Provides a convenient way to set the fields of a ReadWriteFileParams object when creating a new instance, following the Builder pattern.
    ScanResult
    Scan Result class for use in ScannerLibrary methods
